	<h1 class="entry-title post-title">TaskAdapter 2.11.2: better support for JIRA 6+</h1>

<div class="post-meta">
	<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author posted">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.taskadapter.com/2015/11/12/taskadapter-2-11-2-better-support-for-jira-6/" title="TaskAdapter 2.11.2: better support for JIRA 6+" rel="bookmark"><time class="timestamp updated" datetime="2015-11-12T06:12:42+00:00">November 12, 2015</time></a><span class="byline"> by </span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.taskadapter.com/author/admin/" title="View all posts by admin">admin</a></span>
	</div><!-- end of .post-meta -->

				<div class="post-entry">
					<p>TaskAdapter 2.11.2 brings improved support for default settings in JIRA 6 installations.</p>
<p>JIRA 6 has new project templates that have some fields enabled/disabled. The new TaskAdapter version will provide better defaults for JIRA synchronization configs.</p>

					
									</div>
				<!-- end of .post-entry -->

